metadata.name: EAT SHiT AND DiE
metadata.description:
Proud to share the first in the "Watching" collection:  
a study that aims to capture candid moments observed through subjects.  

What captivated me at the time that I took this photo was the story being told through the jacket alone. "EAT SHiT AND DiE" written on the back as, from the shadows, he watches a band joyfully perform together on Bourbon Street.

Shot on 35mm Tri-X 400.
